highlights.text: Dandelions by Ruth B. has been on Top Songs Imphal the longest, at 53 weeks straight.
Justin Bieber has the most spots on Top Songs Imphal. Ghost is the highest at #6.
Be With You by Akon is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Imphal, up 35 spots at #33.
Raabta by Pritam and Arijit Singh is the highest new entry on Top Songs Imphal at #69.
